## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of existing literature. The dynamic nature of innovation systems means that new classifications and frameworks may emerge, which are not covered in this report. Additionally, the interpretation of innovation systems can vary significantly across different academic and practical contexts, leading to potential biases in the findings.